This report includes salaries for employees of other public agencies for which Scott County provides payroll services, including: the Scott County Assessorâ€™s Office, the Scott County Library, the Emergency Management Agency (EMA) and the Scott Emergency Communication Center (SECC). Each employee is listed alphabetically. In addition to wages listed below, employees have the following fringe benefits available to them depending on their FTE status: Medical, Dental, Prescription Drug, Optical, Long Term Disability and Life Insurance, paid vacation and sick leave, retirement contributions, and reimbursement of continuing education. Specific questions about salaries and benefits may be directed to the Scott County Auditor.
